<p>Mon. Mar 4<br/>Received Letter from Mr Bradley thanking me for Particulars of Charley's death, who was killed near Westhock Ridge, on Fri Sept 21/19. <br/>Com. Letter No 11 to B.E.</p>
<p>Tues. 5<br/>Bert the Chef finished up. "Yank" is taking on the Job, with "Darkey" to help him.</p>
<p>Finished Letter No 11.</p>
<p>Wed. 6<br/>"Snowy" returned from Leave only 1 day A.W.L.</p>
<p>Thurs. May 7<br/>The Depot Band is away in London, and the Formal dinner went off without it. It seemed very strange.</p>
<p>To everybody's surprise "Woody" "shouted" for all hands after the "Shivoo" was over.</p>
<p>Got Letter from Lizzie Rowley.</p>
